ampaign with choice based missions\n- Combat Theater Mode\n- Landing Competition Mode\n- Free Flight Mode\n- Optimized Specifically for the Oculus Go\n- And more!", "short_description": "Flying Aces is a story based virtual reality experience unlike any other. You will experience what it\u2019s like to train to become a navy pilot. As gamers, we search for experiences that aren\u2019t possible in our daily lives. With Navy Pilot Simulator, we\u2019re able to bring the armchair pilot into the cockpit of a fighter jet."}]}, "developer_name": "TAS Systems Corp", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://tasappsystems.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "TAS Systems Corp", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.flightsystemsllc.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["FLYING", "SIMULATION", "ACTION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "472797544571205"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982467_2395243027204915_2735773453201178624_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ix4aJfefr8cQ7kNvgHEIzpv&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAJi8xNlb_0Z56qPAgUGPUia_o2Yl20HGssGFxfzfRfog&oe=66D44A1B"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Flying Aces: Navy Pilot Simulator", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1560358800, "lastRevision